Nina: I told you I'm taking her
Nina: You didn't believe me
Nina: Now look at you, coming to me on your knees
Nina: So I take it you want to watch over little Maple?
- I'm joining for my own reasons [#blackheart]
	set Story.black_heart += 1
	Player: I'm joining for my own reasons
	Nina: Hmm?
	Nina: And what might those reasons be
	Player: I don't need to tell you
