	Nina: Poor thing
	Nina: You should really take my advice and buzz off
	Nina: It's seriously going to hurt you
	Player: I don't care
	Nina: 🙄
	Nina: Fucking annoying
Nina: Well anyway, I am obligated to tell you the rules
Nina: You know what you need right?
Nina: You got someone's panties already or you just wasting my time?
Player: I don't
Nina: So why the fuck did you text me in the first place then?
Nina: Are you stupid?
Player: I want yours
Nina: ...
Nina: ......
Nina: You want MY panties?
Player: That's what I'm here for
Nina: 🤣
Nina: You know what, maybe I underestimated you
Nina: You're far worse than a hopeless stupid boy
Nina: It's honestly so funny
Nina: img: nina/12
Nina: Look how hard I'm laughing
Nina: Jeez fuck, I can barely breathe
Nina: I'll give you that you're entertaining though
Player: So is that a yes?
Nina: You know no one's ever asked for mine right?
Nina: You might genuinely be the stupidest person I've ever met
Nina: ...
Nina: Fuck it
Nina: I was trying to be nice at first and look out for you
Player: That's you being nice?
Nina: Mhmm, but now that you've seriously made a clown out of yourself
Nina: And came with your tail between your legs
Nina: I want to watch you get real hurt since you didn't listen to a single one of my warning
Nina: So sure, I'll give you my panties
Nina: I'll send someone over to your room with it
Player: You know where I live?
Nina: Pfft please, like I give a fuck about the dump that you live in
Nina: But the little cuck boys do errands for us sometimes, they'll figure it out
Nina: You'll get them before tomorrow, should be enough time
Nina: They won't believe someone like you has my panties so you might need to show them this pic
Nina: img: nina/13
Player: Wow you're almost sweet
Nina: Jeez do you ever shut up
Nina: Eugh, you'll probably be a creep with my panties
Nina: Anyway shoo, I don't want to think about you anymore
Nina: I'll have to deal with you later anyway
Player: Thanks Nina
Nina: Whatever
=> END"
